nodes.text: Decorative Varactyl Egg Nog was a beverage that existed in the galaxy. As indicated by the name, it was made from the finest Varactyl eggs. At some point during the Galactic Civil War, a spacer investigated a case of missing Life Day candy for the trader Saun Dann. Dann rewarded the spacer with a choice between a decorative egg nog and a Decorative Fruit Cake.
